data.description: Ask about the Down Payment Assistance Loan Program. Move in with $11,000 and 6.5% interest! Get excited about this opportunity!!! Step into the serenity of your new 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom haven in Manor, Texas. Tucked away with a greenbelt backdrop and no rear neighbors, this almost 2000 sf home is on one of the largest lots with distance from neighbors. Recently painted, it boasts spacious interiors, walk-in closets, and a well-thought-out layout for gatherings. All bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, providing a peaceful retreat. The oversized driveway adds practicality, and the back yard offers a serene escape with its view of the greenbelt. Embrace Manor's local charm and amenities, with downtown Manor nearby, and easy access to Austin for work or leisure. The Briarcreek community is just a short fifteen-minute drive from the Tesla Gigafactory! The location provides a diverse range of amenities, from local parks and restaurants to your very own outdoor haven, ensuring there's something for everyone right at your fingertips. Immerse yourself in Manor’s abundance of parks and natural areas, perfect for play, exercise, or simply enjoying the great outdoors. The neighborhood playground and park are conveniently within walking distance, offering easy access for leisurely strolls. For those seeking more extensive recreational options, the East Metropolitan Park and Blake Manor are just a stone's throw away. This home not only offers comfort and style but also invites you to experience the vibrant community surrounding it. Welcome to 11421 Hungry Horse– where convenience, nature, and community seamlessly come together!
